snippet.title: Aliens: Fireteam Elite - Announce Trailer
snippet.description: Introducing Aliens: Fireteam Elite, the next-gen, cooperative third-person survival shooter inspired by the blockbuster Alien franchise. Coming to PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X, Xbox One and Steam in Summer 2021! Learn more at AliensFireteamElite.com!
